Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世之初 冥冥之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning, there was darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着一声爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量 - 终极星系变形者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Energy-- the ultimate galactic transformer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒地从一种形式变为另一种形式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}forever morphing from one form to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它驱动我们的星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It powers our planet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及宇宙间的万物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and everything else in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它到底是什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它究竟来自哪里？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Where did it all come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们如何获得更多？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And how do we get more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量既不能创造也不能消灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Energy can be neither created nor destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只能从一种形态转换成另一种形态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It can only be transformed from one type to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种转换有时会在黑洞这样的天体中变得很极端\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This transformation sometimes goes to the extremes in objects like black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来文明能够利用那种能量么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could a future civilization harness that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么利索的办法 既扔掉了垃圾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What a neat way to get rid of your garbage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时又解决了你的能源危机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and solve your energy crisis, all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们宇宙间的能量最后转移到了别的地方 咋办呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what if our universe's energy was transferred to another place in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有通道打通了平行宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What if a passageway opens up to a parallel universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流走了一些能量 又当如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and bleeds off some of that energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命将无法承受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life wouldn't be able to withstand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能量的故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the story of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你自家后院的大爆炸开始讲起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the Big Bang to your own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你的爱车充足能量 随我们寻踪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Charge up your engines as we follow the trail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙间的极端能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of extreme energy in the universe.
